    <p class="footnotetext">A.  but I think it was someplace around 1987 or something like that.</p>

    <p class="footnotetext">Q. So what would have been the prescription deadline?</p>

    <p class="footnotetext">A. Prescription would have been about a year after they stopped paying him for his worker's
